'''道格拉斯·瓦倫丁'''（{{lang-en|Douglas Valentine}}，{{bd|1949年||}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]作家，撰有數本[[非虛構作品|非小說類書籍]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Douglas Valentine|url=https://go.authorsguild.org/members/2394|accessdate=2021-02-01|publisher=The Authors Guild|language=en}}</ref>。

他的知名作品為1990年出版的《鳳凰行動：美國在越南的恐怖活動》（''The Phoenix Program: America’s Use of Terror in Vietnam''），探討了美國[[中情局|中情局]]在[[越戰|越戰]]期間的行動<ref>{{Cite web|title=The CIA, Narcotics & Underworld: Doug Valentine IV|url=https://www.scoop.co.nz/stories/HL0708/S00242/the-cia-narcotics-underworld-doug-valentine-iv.htm|accessdate=2021-02-01|date=2007-08-19|publisher=Scoop News|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1990/10/21/books/body-count-was-their-most-important-product.html|title=Body Count Was Their Most Important Product|date=1990-10-21|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2021-02-01|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702010159/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/10/21/books/body-count-was-their-most-important-product.html|archivedate=2015-07-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Inside the Organized Crime Syndicate known as the CIA: an Interview with Douglas Valentine|url=https://covertactionmagazine.com/2019/11/21/inside-the-organized-crime-syndicate-known-as-the-cia-an-interview-with-douglas-valentine/|accessdate=2021-02-01|date=2019-11-21|last=Boghosian|first=Heidi|work=CovertAction Magazine|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Douglas Valentine’s CIA vs. Donald Trump’s CIA|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/douglas-valentines-cia-vs-donald-trumps-cia_b_58a615cae4b0b0e1e0e20877|accessdate=2021-02-01|date=2017-02-16|last=Schreiber|first=Brad|work=HuffPost|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Whose Side Is the CIA On?|url=https://whowhatwhy.org/2018/09/06/whose-side-is-the-cia-on/|accessdate=2021-02-01|date=2018-09-06|publisher=WhoWhatWhy|language=en}}</ref>。2017年，他出版了另一部有關中情局的著作《The CIA as Organized Crime》<ref name=":1" />。

瓦倫丁是{{le|全美作家協會|Authors Guild}}會員<ref name=":0" />。

